<topic id='business_definition_youth_detention_accommodation.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Youth Detention Accommodation - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_detention_accommodation">Youth Detention Accommodation</xref>
 is a type of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_accommodation">ACCOMMODATION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_detention_accommodation">Youth Detention Accommodation</xref>
 provides 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_accommodation">ACCOMMODATION</xref>
 and care for children and young people who have been detained or sentenced by the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_justice_board">Youth Justice Board</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_justice_board">YJB</xref>
).  </p>
  <p>
Types of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_detention_accommodation">Youth Detention Accommodation</xref>
 include:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_secure_children_s_home">Secure Children's Home</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_secure_training_centre">Secure Training Centre</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_young_offender_institution__15-17_">Young Offender Institutions (15-17)</xref>
            <p>.</p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_youth_detention_accommodation">Youth Detention Accommodation</xref>
, see the :  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_youth_justice_board">Youth Justice Board</xref>
            <p>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
                <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/manage-bail-and-remand/manage-bail-and-remands-section-3-case-management-guidance"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Guidance Manage bail and remands: section 3 case management guidance</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
Youth Justice Legal Centre website at: 
                <xref href="https://yjlc.uk/youth-detention-accommodation/"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Youth Detention Accommodation (YDA)</xref>
.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>

</body>
